 Gibson与MERC合作推出了限量版Mod Indred Merch Collection https://www.nme.com/news/music/gibson-teams-up-with-merc-to-to-launch-launch-imimited-edition-mod-mod-inspired-merch-collection-3841990?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = gibson-teams-up-with-to-merc-to-merc-to-launch-launch-limimimited-mod-mod-mod inspired-merch收集Liberty DunworthThu, 27 Feb 2025 15:57:15 +0000 Music NewsNewsModsPunkhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3841990 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP-main@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Gibson X Merc与Kid Kapichi合作。学分：吉布森" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP-main@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP-main@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP-main@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP-main@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP-main@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP-main@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他们在Kid Kapichi的帮助下推出了新系列</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gibson-teams-up-with-merc-to-launch-limited-edition-mod-inspired-merch-collection-3841990">Gibson Post与MERC合作，推出了限量版Mod Indrepired Merch Collection，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP-main@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Gibson X Merc与Kid Kapichi合作。学分：吉布森" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP-main@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP-main@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP-main@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP-main@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP-main@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP-main@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>吉布森（Gibson）与英国服装品牌MERC联手创建了限量版的Mod-Indreps商品运行。查看下面的集合。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kid-kapichi-and-madness-suggs-talk-new-single-zombie-nation-and-the-impact-of-the-specials-terry-hall-3593758">Kid Kapichi和Madness“ Suggs谈论新单曲“僵尸民族”和特惠的Terry Hall的影响</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>这家标志性的吉他品牌已与该公司加入了新的Merc X Gibson Capsule Collection，该系列专门在伦敦的Gibson车库有限的时期可用。</p><p>该系列设计的目的是强调音乐与时尚之间的牢固联系，包括五个。这些是“传奇人物哈灵顿夹克”，“ Luthier Polo衫”，“桥梁连帽运动衫”，“即兴T恤”和“ Tone” T恤。</p><p> “ MERC很高兴与Gibson合作，我们很荣幸能展示一个胶囊系列，以体现本质并庆祝这两个品牌的丰富遗产，” MERC董事总经理Sas Alavi在一份新声明中说。 “该系列经过精心设计，可以无缝地融合Merc和Gibson的美学，同时吸引现代敏感性，从而创造出与时尚爱好者和吉他爱好者都产生共鸣的作品。” </p><figure id="attachment_3841991" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3841991" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3841991" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Gibson X Merc与Kid Kapichi合作" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3841991" class="wp-caption-text"> Gibson X Merc与Kid Kapichi合作。学分：吉布森</figcaption></figure><p>该系列还借助上升的朋克摇滚乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kid-kapichi">Kid Kapichi</a>宣布，他们被选为“当选择一位在2025年体现朋克摇滚生活方式并展示胶囊系列的艺术家时，他们是自然而然的选择”。</p><p> Kid Kapichi和Blue Stragglers一起参加了本周早些时候在Eastcastle Street的Gibson车库，以推出新范围，并在商店提供了各种表演。</p><p> “很高兴与两个标志性品牌紧密合作。随着时间的流逝，我们自然而然地陷入了吉布森吉他的圈速，因为我认为他们的声音是我们创造的音乐无与伦比的，” Kid Kapichi说。 “因此，与他们合作多个项目是一种荣幸。</p><p> “当我们被要求与新合作合作时，说&#39;是&#39;是一个简单的决定。 Merc总是为60年代的美好重现美丽的物品。与音乐和乐队密切相关的一种，我们一生都热爱我们的一生。我们受到了这些乐队的影响，衣服也与之齐头并进。”</p><p>查看下面范围的更多图像，并在<a href="https://www.gibson.com/en-GB/garage-london?srsltid=AfmBOop5H3oH5xcxYRFN-zNmoCaabwyElWkGm3qjRlJTAIzvRfVvfoN_" target="_blank" rel="noopener">伦敦的吉布森车库</a>中独家找到完整的收藏。 </p><figure id="attachment_3841992" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3841992" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3841992" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-jacket@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Gibson X Merc合作。学分：吉布森" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-jacket@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-jacket@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-jacket@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-jacket@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-jacket@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-jacket@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3841992" class="wp-caption-text"> Gibson X Merc合作。学分：吉布森</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3841994" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3841994" style="width: 